---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Performances | Workshops | Preaching | Scripture Alive"
  description="Scripture Alive, a ministry that seeks to engage people with the Word of Truth to impact real lives."
  ogImage="https://scripturealive.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/scripturealive.png"
>

  <!-- HERO SECTION with video background -->
  <section class="relative h-screen flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
    <video
      class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover z-0"
      autoplay
      muted
      playsinline
      loop
      aria-hidden="true"
    >
      <source src="https://scripturealive.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/63c9566f010aa46eb2df7c75.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
    </video>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/50 z-10"></div>
    <div class="relative z-20 text-center text-white px-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-4 text-white drop-shadow-lg" style="font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;">
        Making Scripture Unforgettable
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl mb-10 text-white drop-shadow-md font-normal" style="font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;">
        Performances | Workshops | Speaking
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="bg-primary text-black font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded text-base transition-all duration-300 hover:opacity-90"
        >
          Invite Jeremy
        </a>
        <a
          href="/referjeremy"
          class="border-2 border-white text-white hover:bg-white hover:text-black font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded text-base transition-all duration-300"
        >
          Refer Jeremy
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- DEDICATED TO PROCLAIMING SECTION -->
  <section class="bg-white pt-16 pb-8 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold leading-tight" style="color: #FBC215; font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;">
        Dedicated to Proclaiming the Word with Creativity and Conviction
      </h2>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FOUR FEATURES SECTION -->
  <section class="bg-white py-8 px-4 pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
      <!-- Pure Scripture -->
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center p-6 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10" style="color: #FBC215;" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M18 2H6c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v16c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h12c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V4c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm-2 14H8v-2h8v2zm0-4H8v-2h8v2zm0-4H8V6h8v2z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-base font-bold mb-2" style="color: #FBC215; font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;">Pure Scripture</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Every performance is quoted word for word from the Bible.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Skillfully Dramatized -->
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center p-6 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10" style="color: #FBC215;" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M11.99 2C6.47 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.47 10 9.99 10C17.52 22 22 17.52 22 12S17.52 2 11.99 2zM12 20c-4.42 0-8-3.58-8-8s3.58-8 8-8 8 3.58 8 8-3.58 8-8 8zm3.5-9c.83 0 1.5-.67 1.5-1.5S16.33 8 15.5 8 14 8.67 14 9.5s.67 1.5 1.5 1.5zm-7 0c.83 0 1.5-.67 1.5-1.5S9.33 8 8.5 8 7 8.67 7 9.5 7.67 11 8.5 11zm3.5 6.5c2.33 0 4.31-1.46 5.11-3.5H6.89c.8 2.04 2.78 3.5 5.11 3.5z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-base font-bold mb-2" style="color: #FBC215; font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;">Skillfully Dramatized</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">A high-quality theatrical production makes Scripture leap off of the page.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Impacting Lives -->
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center p-6 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10" style="color: #FBC215;" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M16 11c1.66 0 2.99-1.34 2.99-3S17.66 5 16 5c-1.66 0-3 1.34-3 3s1.34 3 3 3zm-8 0c1.66 0 2.99-1.34 2.99-3S9.66 5 8 5C6.34 5 5 6.34 5 8s1.34 3 3 3zm0 2c-2.33 0-7 1.17-7 3.5V19h14v-2.5c0-2.33-4.67-3.5-7-3.5zm8 0c-.29 0-.62.02-.97.05 1.16.84 1.97 1.97 1.97 3.45V19h6v-2.5c0-2.33-4.67-3.5-7-3.5z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-base font-bold mb-2" style="color: #FBC215; font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;">Impacting Lives</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">People regularly say how moved they are and how it helps them better understand the Bible.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Unique and Memorable -->
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center p-6 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10" style="color: #FBC215;" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M12 2a5 5 0 1 0 0 10A5 5 0 0 0 12 2zm0 12c-5.33 0-8 2.67-8 4v2h16v-2c0-1.33-2.67-4-8-4z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-base font-bold mb-2" style="color: #FBC215; font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;">Unique and Memorable</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Your audience will never forget when Scripture is dramatically presented!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SERVICE TILES SECTION -->
  <section class="bg-white px-4 pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
      <!-- Scripture Performances -->
      <a href="/performances" class="relative rounded overflow-hidden shadow group block h-48">
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300"
          style="background-image: url('https://assets.spiritmediapublishing.com/scripture-alive/2107248e6e6621d6b4fe5c38c18c8cd5_1200_80-rdodoupy1h2rw6xw4mrrs0ezpy6gn7vm8zl0kghkru.webp');"
        ></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/40"></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="text-white text-xl font-semibold italic drop-shadow-lg" style="font-family: 'Dancing Script', cursive;">Scripture Performances</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <!-- Scripture Memory Workshops -->
      <a href="/workshops" class="relative rounded overflow-hidden shadow group block h-48">
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300"
          style="background-image: url('https://assets.spiritmediapublishing.com/scripture-alive/7dea0315c3929177440f5d9a90340ce8_1200_80-rdodoupy1h2rw6xw4mrrs0ezpy6gn7vm8zl0kghkru.webp');"
        ></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/40"></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="text-white text-xl font-semibold italic drop-shadow-lg" style="font-family: 'Dancing Script', cursive;">Scripture Memory Workshops</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <!-- Guest Preaching -->
      <a href="/guestpreaching" class="relative rounded overflow-hidden shadow group block h-48">
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300"
          style="background-image: url('https://assets.spiritmediapublishing.com/scripture-alive/f851f13fa9d3e0e5887f74730556c3d0_1200_80-rdodoupy1h2rw6xw4mrrs0ezpy6gn7vm8zl0kghkru.webp');"
        ></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/40"></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="text-white text-xl font-semibold italic drop-shadow-lg" style="font-family: 'Dancing Script', cursive;">Guest Preaching</span>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TESTIMONIALS SECTION -->
  <section class="bg-white py-16 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto relative">
      <div class="testimonial-wrapper overflow-hidden">
        <div class="testimonial-track flex transition-transform duration-500" id="testimonialTrack">

          <!-- Slide 1 -->
          <div class="testimonial-slide min-w-full text-center px-8">
            <blockquote class="text-gray-700 text-base italic leading-relaxed mb-8" style="font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;">
              "Jeremy transports you back in time and into the pages of Scripture. He has uncanny ability to embody all the characters in a story and keep you highly engaged. I highly recommend him when you seek to have people connect to God's Word in an entirely new way."
            </blockquote>
            <div>
              <p class="font-bold text-base" style="color: #1a3a5c;">Tami Heim, President and CEO</p>
              <p class="font-medium text-sm" style="color: #FBC215;">Christian Leadership Alliance</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Slide 2 -->
          <div class="testimonial-slide min-w-full text-center px-8">
            <blockquote class="text-gray-700 text-base italic leading-relaxed mb-8" style="font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;">
              "I strongly encourage pastors and ministry leaders to utilize the ministry gifts of Jeremy Kluth. There's nothing like hearing God's Word memorized and expressed with passion. Your people will be inspired."
            </blockquote>
            <div>
              <p class="font-bold text-base" style="color: #1a3a5c;">Roy Patterson, Community Relationship Director</p>
              <p class="font-medium text-sm" style="color: #FBC215;">Moody Bible Institute, Chicago IL</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Slide 3 -->
          <div class="testimonial-slide min-w-full text-center px-8">
            <blockquote class="text-gray-700 text-base italic leading-relaxed mb-8" style="font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;">
              "Jeremy Kluth is a gifted communicator who brings Scripture to life in a way that is both powerful and memorable. His performances have deeply impacted our congregation."
            </blockquote>
            <div>
              <p class="font-bold text-base" style="color: #1a3a5c;">Pastor David Williams</p>
              <p class="font-medium text-sm" style="color: #FBC215;">Grace Community Church</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Slide 4 -->
          <div class="testimonial-slide min-w-full text-center px-8">
            <blockquote class="text-gray-700 text-base italic leading-relaxed mb-8" style="font-family: 'Montserrat